title: Interesting (not particularly problematic) bug.
body:
I was having a terrible game, a few minutes before they ended i was kicked by lee sin back towards tower and knocked into a couple of creeps which got stuck in this spot until they were killed, didn't attack anyone or anything just bugged out until malphite and lee killed them. 
Slight problem with minion pathing or something? I'm not sure 
Still, thought it was interesting
